<!-- Game Description Table -->

<table class="tablestyle" id="table14" cellspacing="4" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td class="sectional">

<!-- Game Description Header -->
		
		<table class="headertable" id="table15" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="2">
			<tr>
				<td class="headercell">
				<img border="0" src="../../../images/headers/gamedes.jpg" width="240" height="33"></td>
			</tr>
		</table>

<!-- Game Description Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>This Playstation game features 3 different games in just one cd.
                  <br><br>In the first game the player will control a boy and a girl that are sent to another world in which there are onis (demons) and to advance in the game they will have to win different demon billiard games.
                  <br><br>The second game features a group of rebel knights lead by her princess that are trying to stay alive and recover his kingdom. The gameplay is about using up to 6 characters that will use battle tanks to defeat the enemy army.
                  <br><br>The third game is more an educational title in which the player controls a young boy named Joe that will have to solve different kind of puzzles in a futuristic world.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Manufacturer's description:</u><br>
                  <br>Omnibus software packed with adventure game three to one. "Hyakuoni-o and Kyoko" high school girl Kyoko fight monkey jump-Hyakki King, boy Miss resolve any incident in the universe of the future struggle "PRINCESS'S KNIGHTS", much the Knights of iron to save the princess I have recorded three of the "space rescue Jo".
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Features:</u><br>
			<ul><li>Third & first person perspectives.</li>
			<li>2D & 3D graphics</li>
			<li>Cartoon graphics</li>
			<li>SCI-FI & Fantasy themes.</li></ul>
</td>

	</tr>
	</table>
	       	</td>
     </tr>
</table>  

